overview: The Cherokee Strip is off limits to the Rangers, so that is where badman Lemar operates from. When the Rangers capture his brother and the jury sentences him to hang, Lemar starts killing the jurists. Then the scoundrels kidnap the Captain's daughter Doris... Written by Tony Fontana
tagline: FOR LOVE AND JUSTICE The Three Mesquiteers riding hard...fighting for right among lawless men...giving protection to the girl of their choice!
title: Outlaws of Cherokee Trail
